{"tid":2462243,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"文尼迪奧夫齊健身 紅軍粉絲唔高興","createTime":"2021-03-26T01:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T02:33:13.000Z","uid":67225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"14ea46db3a3d43d50944ffe1b62eceec92ab956e","tid":2462243,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:34:21.000Z","msg":"沙迪奧文尼跟迪奧夫一起健身，並出言大讚這位過去跟謝拉特有不少牙齒印的前利物浦前鋒，此舉引起了一眾紅軍球迷的不滿。沙迪奧文尼（Sadio Mane）目前正跟塞內加爾國家隊一起備戰，他早前在社交網絡instagram分享一張跟前塞內加爾國腳迪奧夫（El Hadji Diouf）一起健身的照片，並盛讚對方是塞國歷來的最佳球員，此舉惹來紅軍球迷的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有網民大肆抨擊同樣曾效力過利物浦的迪奧夫：「他是紅軍歷來最糟糕的收購，無禮、可恥的球員，我想知文尼為甚麼會這樣做？」另一名粉絲則說：「對於文尼視迪奧夫為偶像，我每一天仍對此感到憤怒。」有球迷笑指以自己作為不喜歡迪奧夫的按鈕，最終該粉絲短時間內就取得逾700個like，可見紅軍球迷對迪奧夫有多麼不滿。<br />\n<br />\n現年40歲的迪奧夫，2002至04年間曾效力過利物浦，期間上陣79次攻入過6球，表現一般，但效力期間卻屢次跟「神奇隊長」謝拉特發生衝突，絕對不是紅軍粉絲的寵兒。"},{"pid":"f7ccf94ce2a6bee54d86b68688aac6af00c098cc","tid":2462243,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:35:10.000Z","msg":"文尼正一大仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decd282242095ffa09af811ebf4c6197a1e3adbb","tid":2462243,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"同同鄉前輩健身都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c75da0caead8a00dec39e8ac060a343bc897ddb5","tid":2462243,"uid":61228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"同鄉前輩，有交情都唔得？"},{"pid":"2d566a373df849a6e4527555d9cdf6faaa46fc8a","tid":2462243,"uid":27287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:04:05.000Z","msg":"痢狗係特別戇鳩<br />\n同鄉一齊健身都唔撚得"},{"pid":"febcdcaabe2e5c673d3072e22cf6f497e89822d6","tid":2462243,"uid":11694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:15:12.000Z","msg":"痴撚線、你唔妥人關佢咩事，小圈子猁狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6afc8d9965549c38f5ea8b14079d6b46e50a02","tid":2462243,"uid":301523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:17:56.000Z","msg":"Moto？"},{"pid":"b253bad8aac60101558cc75f598b03ec157b4466","tid":2462243,"uid":140363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:19:27.000Z","msg":"佢臭馬還臭馬 但冇迪奧夫 邊有人識塞內加爾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45cfa96a6e9c1f7896b6eddf6feb789adc594243","tid":2462243,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:19:57.000Z","msg":"痢狗真係戇撚鳩。"},{"pid":"9bd5f58e136d415670287cdf13d55951f3945389","tid":2462243,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"decd282242095ffa09af811ebf4c6197a1e3adbb","tid":2462243,"uid":34899,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"同同鄉前輩健身都唔比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:22:28.000Z","msg":"國家隊史上第二嘅射手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b616a94ae354c4d44f3f90c9be083b44304ec05","tid":2462243,"uid":2949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:25:59.000Z","msg":"文尼呢d挑釁既行為，將會令你响利身浦既地位變成零"},{"pid":"2bcb52eb801f4ebeb390a68b27618acee9be3870","tid":2462243,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b616a94ae354c4d44f3f90c9be083b44304ec05","tid":2462243,"uid":2949,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:25:59.000Z","msg":"文尼呢d挑釁既行為，將會令你响利身浦既地位變成零"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:32:12.000Z","msg":"最好唔好啦"},{"pid":"bfa8dc445eb3f1eddb44537526e95e0e335f958f","tid":2462243,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T02:33:13.000Z","msg":"D BLM養唔熟"}]}